Class.ClassComment: UpdatableVTITemplate /** * An abstract implementation of PreparedStatement (JDBC 3.0) that is useful when writing a read-write (updatable) virtual table interface (VTI). This class implements the methods of the JDBC3.0 version of PreparedStatement each one throwing a SQLException with the name of the method. A concrete subclass can then just implement the methods not implemented here and override any methods it needs to implement for correct functionality. */
